00:29:42.897 --> 00:29:46.334 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And the class has a letter that will now be read,

00:29:46.334 --> 00:29:50.805 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and Brother Philip Morgan will do that for us.

00:29:57.812 --> 00:30:01.516 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“To the Governing Body
and the United States Bethel family.

00:30:03.151 --> 00:30:05.954 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Over the course of the past five months,

00:30:05.954 --> 00:30:07.989 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“more than ever before,

00:30:07.989 --> 00:30:11.860 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“we have been tuned to the evidence
of Jehovah’s powerful holy spirit

00:30:11.860 --> 00:30:14.028 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“all around us.

00:30:14.028 --> 00:30:18.566 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“From the day we entered the main lobby
here at the Watchtower Educational Center,

00:30:18.566 --> 00:30:21.469 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“the fruitage of that spirit enveloped us

00:30:21.469 --> 00:30:24.072 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“with love and kindness

00:30:24.072 --> 00:30:28.776 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“through the hospitality
of the United States Bethel family.

00:30:28.776 --> 00:30:31.779 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Without your daily help and encouragement,

00:30:31.779 --> 00:30:36.651 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“we would not have been able to give
such concentrated focus to our studies.

00:30:36.651 --> 00:30:40.154 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We thank you all from the bottom of our hearts!

00:30:41.422 --> 00:30:44.092 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We also have sensed how our instructors

00:30:44.092 --> 00:30:48.129 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“have striven to allow
the holy spirit to shape and mold them,

00:30:48.129 --> 00:30:52.000 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“even as they shared the benefits 
of their own deep study of God’s Word

00:30:52.000 --> 00:30:55.603 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“and experience with us
each day in the classroom.

00:30:56.704 --> 00:31:00.241 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Just like those Jehovah
used to train others in the past,

00:31:00.241 --> 00:31:04.679 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“they imparted to us 
not only the finer points of the truth

00:31:04.679 --> 00:31:07.048 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“but ‘[their] very souls.’

00:31:07.048 --> 00:31:12.053 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“They ‘became . . . beloved to us,’
even as we know we are to them.

00:31:13.154 --> 00:31:16.925 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Perhaps most touching
has been the personal attention

00:31:16.925 --> 00:31:20.361 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“shown to us
by you dear brothers of the Governing Body.

00:31:21.462 --> 00:31:24.332 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“The evidence of Jehovah’s spirit
working through you

00:31:24.332 --> 00:31:27.335 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“is something we will cherish
for the rest of our lives.

00:31:28.436 --> 00:31:31.506 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We realize how much concern
you carry with you

00:31:31.506 --> 00:31:35.176 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“for the entire association
of our brothers worldwide,

00:31:35.176 --> 00:31:37.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“as well as for the many sheeplike ones

00:31:37.312 --> 00:31:40.214 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“yet to be reached with the Kingdom good news.

00:31:40.214 --> 00:31:43.318 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We especially appreciated the fact

00:31:43.318 --> 00:31:47.055 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“that you each took time to spend with our class

00:31:47.055 --> 00:31:52.060 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“and spoke to us
as a father to children to reassure us,

00:31:52.060 --> 00:31:54.862 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“to protect us with reminders,

00:31:54.862 --> 00:31:59.867 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“and to build confidence
that Jehovah will be with us in the days ahead.

00:32:00.568 --> 00:32:03.871 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“And you sent many of your helpers
to do just the same,

00:32:03.871 --> 00:32:05.873 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“which we deeply appreciated.

00:32:07.542 --> 00:32:10.778 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“The apostle Paul
reminded his anointed brothers

00:32:10.778 --> 00:32:15.350 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“that ‘where the spirit of Jehovah is,
there is freedom.’

00:32:15.350 --> 00:32:19.654 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Now more than ever, 
we see evidence of how true that is.

00:32:19.654 --> 00:32:23.725 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“By means of his faithful slave,
the Gilead arrangement,

00:32:23.725 --> 00:32:26.427 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“and this beautiful Bethel family,

00:32:26.427 --> 00:32:28.830 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Jehovah has used his spirit

00:32:28.830 --> 00:32:32.033 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“to free us from any inhibitions,

00:32:32.033 --> 00:32:34.602 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“fears, or hesitations.

00:32:34.602 --> 00:32:38.573 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We feel more prepared
to accomplish whatever work he assigns

00:32:38.573 --> 00:32:43.111 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“by relying
on that most powerful force in the universe

00:32:43.111 --> 00:32:45.947 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“—God’s holy spirit.

00:32:45.947 --> 00:32:48.750 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Along with the rest of God’s family of servants,

00:32:48.750 --> 00:32:50.952 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“heavenly and earthly,

00:32:50.952 --> 00:32:54.622 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“we are ready to follow the leading of that spirit

00:32:54.622 --> 00:32:58.226 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“wherever it will send us in the days ahead!

00:32:58.226 --> 00:33:00.228 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“With heartfelt love,

00:33:00.228 --> 00:33:02.764 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“we are your brothers and sisters

00:33:02.764 --> 00:33:06.567 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of the 146th class of Gilead.”

00:33:11.906 --> 00:33:15.376 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Graduates
—that has a nice sound to it, doesn’t it?

00:33:15.376 --> 00:33:17.412 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It came quickly.

00:33:17.412 --> 00:33:21.315 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, I’ve been asked to give
a few comments here at the end

00:33:21.315 --> 00:33:26.120 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and to include this point,
so I’ll begin with it:

00:33:26.120 --> 00:33:28.856 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Back in 2011,

00:33:28.856 --> 00:33:33.661 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the Governing Body adjusted
the objective of Gilead training

00:33:33.661 --> 00:33:37.632 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in order to help further strengthen and stabilize

00:33:37.632 --> 00:33:40.201 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the field and branch organization.

00:33:40.201 --> 00:33:42.203 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And as a result,

00:33:42.203 --> 00:33:45.239 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we have seen
Jehovah’s rich blessing on this adjustment

00:33:45.239 --> 00:33:49.911 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as it relates 
to branch and country committees worldwide.

00:33:49.911 --> 00:33:54.916 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Since the time 
of the graduation of the 132nd class,

00:33:54.916 --> 00:33:59.821 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
182 graduates
have been appointed to a committee,

00:33:59.821 --> 00:34:04.826 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
either during or sometime
after their training at Gilead.

00:34:04.826 --> 00:34:08.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That’s a wonderful fact, isn’t it?

00:34:08.229 --> 00:34:13.234 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And it’s something
that is really proving to be a blessing

00:34:13.234 --> 00:34:16.971 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to the worldwide field
and to our dear brotherhood and, above all,

00:34:16.971 --> 00:34:20.374 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in upholding and honoring Jehovah’s name.

00:34:20.374 --> 00:34:23.077 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So this is a marvelous arrangement.

00:34:23.077 --> 00:34:26.380 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now with this in mind,
just for a couple of minutes,

00:34:26.380 --> 00:34:29.684 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I want to give
concluding comments on this topic:

00:34:29.684 --> 00:34:33.554 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Maintain Your ‘Shield of Faith.’”

00:34:33.554 --> 00:34:36.424 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You see, when you
are settled into your assignments

00:34:36.424 --> 00:34:40.061 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—perhaps with new responsibilities—

00:34:40.061 --> 00:34:42.730 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
remember to remain watchful

00:34:42.730 --> 00:34:46.434 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
so that you stay focused
on what is most important,

00:34:46.434 --> 00:34:49.871 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
namely, the doing of Jehovah’s will.

00:34:49.871 --> 00:34:54.475 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The danger can come
when we feel that we’ve achieved most

00:34:54.475 --> 00:34:57.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or even all of our spiritual goals.

00:34:57.645 --> 00:35:00.047 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If we allow that to happen,

00:35:00.047 --> 00:35:03.084 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
our interests could turn to other things.

00:35:03.084 --> 00:35:06.053 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
For example, if we lose sight of the point

00:35:06.053 --> 00:35:09.590 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and the purpose
behind what it means to follow Jesus,

00:35:09.590 --> 00:35:14.295 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we could start to center our thoughts
on other goals (it could happen),

00:35:14.295 --> 00:35:16.464 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
perhaps even material things.

00:35:16.464 --> 00:35:18.466 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But don’t let this happen to you.

00:35:18.466 --> 00:35:21.736 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Keep your shield of faith strong.

00:35:21.736 --> 00:35:23.738 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In Bible times,

00:35:23.738 --> 00:35:28.176 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
soldiers repaired and secured
their shields between battles.

00:35:28.176 --> 00:35:32.647 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They treasured
those protective pieces of armor.

00:35:32.647 --> 00:35:35.983 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Because their shields
were often covered with leather,

00:35:35.983 --> 00:35:40.388 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the soldiers would rub oil
on to the shield to help preserve it

00:35:40.388 --> 00:35:44.158 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and to keep the metal parts free from rust.

00:35:44.158 --> 00:35:47.962 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If a soldier found damage or weakness,
what did he do?

00:35:47.962 --> 00:35:51.532 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He immediately made
the needed repairs to his shield.

00:35:51.532 --> 00:35:56.137 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In this way,
he was always ready for the next battle.

00:35:56.137 --> 00:35:58.940 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We need to keep this up in a spiritual way.

00:35:58.940 --> 00:36:01.843 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Over time, a brother or sister

00:36:01.843 --> 00:36:04.478 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
might lay down his or her shield of faith

00:36:04.478 --> 00:36:07.849 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and go after things that have no lasting value.

00:36:07.849 --> 00:36:12.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Devil wants nothing more
than for us to neglect our faith

00:36:12.854 --> 00:36:15.790 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and open up our heart to his attacks.

00:36:15.790 --> 00:36:17.792 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And for this reason,

00:36:17.792 --> 00:36:20.795 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Paul, the apostle Paul,
was inspired to say

00:36:20.795 --> 00:36:24.866 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that those who go
after material riches, for instance,

00:36:24.866 --> 00:36:28.436 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
would cultivate
“many senseless and harmful desires.”

00:36:28.436 --> 00:36:31.472 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He added:
“Flee from these things.”

00:36:31.472 --> 00:36:36.444 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You see, ultimately,
we are each responsible for how large

00:36:36.444 --> 00:36:40.548 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and how strong our shield of faith proves to be.

00:36:40.548 --> 00:36:43.918 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, we show that we are strengthening

00:36:43.918 --> 00:36:46.287 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
our faith in Jehovah and his Son

00:36:46.287 --> 00:36:50.691 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
when we take time
to continue caring for our spiritual needs.

00:36:50.691 --> 00:36:53.628 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So don’t take liberties with your spiritual routine

00:36:53.628 --> 00:36:57.999 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
just because you’ve graduated
from this wonderful school.

00:36:57.999 --> 00:37:00.334 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Don’t become self-satisfied

00:37:00.334 --> 00:37:04.438 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
because of resting
on a privilege you may come to enjoy.

00:37:04.438 --> 00:37:06.841 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That’s not the point of it, is it?

00:37:06.841 --> 00:37:09.443 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Keep growing as a spiritual person

00:37:09.443 --> 00:37:13.014 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
by giving attention to your faith day by day.

00:37:13.014 --> 00:37:15.316 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Oil and preserve your shield

00:37:15.316 --> 00:37:18.352 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
by regularly attending Christian meetings

00:37:18.352 --> 00:37:22.590 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and speaking about Jehovah’s name
and his Kingdom to others.

00:37:22.590 --> 00:37:27.595 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Also, maintain strong faith
by reading God’s Word every day

00:37:27.595 --> 00:37:29.830 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—as you’ve been encouraged to
and have been doing—

00:37:29.830 --> 00:37:32.767 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and applying its counsel in all that you do.

00:37:32.767 --> 00:37:36.504 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Imitate the Christ every step of the way.

00:37:36.504 --> 00:37:40.608 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In this way, you’ll be like
the victorious soldier who worked hard

00:37:40.608 --> 00:37:45.146 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to care for his shield
and other valuable pieces of armor.

00:37:45.947 --> 00:37:48.349 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Hold your shield firmly in front of you.

00:37:48.349 --> 00:37:51.452 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Use it to protect your figurative heart

00:37:51.452 --> 00:37:54.021 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and to defend Jehovah’s pure worship.

00:37:54.021 --> 00:37:56.457 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Keep it well maintained,

00:37:56.457 --> 00:38:01.362 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and you will always be ready
to “fight the fine fight of the faith.”

00:38:01.362 --> 00:38:04.298 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah and his Son will bless you for it.

